Miss Sandy Cowell said on 20/Dec/21

Let's spare a thought for Emmanuel Ogabi, the 26-year-old young man who was stabbed to death when he went for a walk late in the evening.

Emmanuel was laid to rest today, and his sisters, Grace and Susan, like Brooke Kinsella, whose own brother was murdered in the same evil way, are speaking out against this disgusting crime.

Miss Sandy Cowell said on 26/Mar/19

What a brave girl Brooke is, dealing with the wicked killing of her brother by campaigning against this sort of dreadful violence.

I can't see myself having been so brave if that happened to me.

Small in stature she may be, but Brooke has the courage and resolve of 10 men. My heart goes out to her for all the good work she has done since the terrible incident.

5ft.
